title: Daily Review with Clay and Buck - Jan 11 2022

description:
Wisconsin Senator Ron Johnson on why covid played a big part in his decision to run again. Stacey Abrams blows off Biden and Harris in Georgia -- and Buck's mom dances with Ralph Macchio! Ted Cruz torches FBI on role in Jan. 6th riot. Ohio Representative Jim Jordan on the weaponization of the government against the people.
